'''北韓離脫住民定着支援事務所'''（{{朝|諺=북한이탈주민정착지원사무소|漢=北韓離脫住民定着支援事務所|羅=Bukhan italjumin jeongchakjiwon-samuso|名=南}}，{{lang-en|Settlement Support Center for North Korean Refugees}}），又稱'''統一院'''（{{kor|link=no|諺=하나원|漢=하나院|羅=Hanawon}}），是[[大韓民國|大韓民國]]主要的[[脫北者|脫北者]]再教育機構，1999年8月建於[[京畿道|京畿道]][[安城市_(韓國)|安城市]]，隶属于[[统一部|统一部]]。據[[芭芭拉·德米克|芭芭拉·德米克]]《[[我們最幸福：北韓人民的真實生活|我們最幸福：北韓人民的真實生活]]》一書記載，統一院兼有培訓學校和中途客棧性質，旨在通過三個月的全方位培訓，使脫北者適應韓國生活，並融入韓國社會。<ref name="Demick 2010 249">{{cite book|last=Demick|first=Barbara|title=Nothing to envy: ordinary lives in North Korea|url=https://archive.org/details/nothingtoenvyord00demi_0|year=2010|publisher=Spiegel & Grau|location=New York|isbn=0385523912|pages=[https://archive.org/details/nothingtoenvyord00demi_0/page/249 249]|edition=Spiegel & Grau trade}}</ref>然而許多脫北者離院後仍然不能獨立適應充滿競爭的韓國社會，因此仍需[[自由北韓|自由北韓]]、[[新祖為|新祖為]]等[[非政府組織|非政府組織]]的援助。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://blogs.cfr.org/asia/2011/05/01/delivering-social-justice-for-north-korean-refugees-in-south-korea-the-role-of-civil-society-and-opportunities-for-u-s-south-korea-cooperation/ |title=Delivering Social Justice for North Korean Refugees in South Korea:  The Role of Civil Society and Opportunities for U.S.-South Korean Cooperation |last1=Park |first1=Gil-sung |last2=Moon |first2=Chun-sang |publisher=Council on Foreign Relations |date=May 1, 2011 |accessdate=March 9, 2015 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150910084512/http://blogs.cfr.org/asia/2011/05/01/delivering-social-justice-for-north-korean-refugees-in-south-korea-the-role-of-civil-society-and-opportunities-for-u-s-south-korea-cooperation/ |archive-date=2015-09-10 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

